title: William Johnstone -Eagles 07 Cry of Eagles
description: Falcon MacCallister roams the West, and with a destiny as wide and unsure as the open range, he is a loner. But to those who know him, he is a legend. In a split-second hook and draw, Falcon ends the life of a young gunslick...and once again, becomes the most wanted man in the West. Now, from the Arizona border to the shadows of the Dragoon Mountains to the burning trail of Apache rage, he must fend off a ruthless posse that has sworn vengeance.
